{"tid":2505493,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Diy洗冷氣","createTime":"2021-04-26T15:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T13:39:14.000Z","uid":361936,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9934ecd0fa76ac2aefe628322115854b58664b67","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"上年已經post過一次<br />\n由武漢肺炎，到而家英國肺炎<br />\n剛好一年，今年自己買番水壓機，唔洗再問人借工具，又再洗過<br />\n一年時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW3fvmR6aXQqLKCRe3pf4nN968hwgNDp6hd51JAvS7HMa?filename=A6kKKmh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6kKKmh.png&h=37d8efb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ed4acf0f9f21085664ba873a4eecb91ad475fad","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"唔錯,大力過worx水槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQQsv6YaxKehXH3nmQQmz2snbKTMJHfxTPqCKAbNpPr6N?filename=TGDDOOM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGDDOOM.png&h=5f8cce96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fa0d12f6e9a016bea36d2f3374efe9dd07fee2d","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdDzS7N6AhmanwimzFWWhcjAZ2A4rdFS7ceuVtgq9szXD?filename=LO9STmx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLO9STmx.png&h=d328e3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeLrXN18LteEHnahst4TC2uCg41sZvm3x8LFYxQPWsKet?filename=XEWua8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEWua8y.png&h=439681d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就禁用水壓機，已經清唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPxAqwKLQJbWxHaTmCZLC9V8utYpJvVYi6oTNkyRNe8gY?filename=NAv3fAq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAv3fAq.png&h=cd0faded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一部機用coil水，太多毒氣冇映<br />\n第二部機只係用藍威寶<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQzqMmE1s39FygEnz2SSWJZhWP6WCboGmsw9vPa6gLZFF?filename=cOQrdnv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOQrdnv.png&h=6560c9d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca12eb6c9f68f93c693bec0d21e0b399a18df07f","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"hea洗，同用心分別就係藥水溝多啲水，過水又可以hea洗<br />\n由奇worx水槍冇力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用心洗就比較濃藥水，大水量，慢慢過水<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV5rjSAd3TmR5qLMPZc9J6gmjaDBpzXYCLpi9wNdy4g2y?filename=UGzjyp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGzjyp0.png&h=48411716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUBtDTdPPaUjLoAhJznAknPYEeJdaJVm4ixagq5cQwwUx?filename=VGS9bdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGS9bdK.png&h=8fbc8c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPfde7m4crQw4yctryyrnXY8enZSy2PPRLGSWcGLksAMF?filename=agbubdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagbubdQ.png&h=4c7cf504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNhQUnEAvKL7dkX1229UhntVWtVxkSy4RdbqkFcqPX81V?filename=Drwenky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrwenky.png&h=79c8fee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTYRAd7ys9rSjSNj9oY6SJKv1eXhUijyHfP5adMXSFAwX?filename=ZibxTsh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZibxTsh.png&h=ae2e5e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTQhJ38CXbzzuptL4cE9JdvJLzD7L2FyZzRwutfEZ4Bt8?filename=qVd4Ky1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVd4Ky1.png&h=36f6b38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n透光無塵<br />\n<br />\n之後個D，都係check下有冇入水漏電，上年post過，今年唔映<br />\n<br />\n過多排搞埋Fd D分體再post"},{"pid":"2deef7de40ee0a5f36560843c672148c47533119","tid":2505493,"uid":72316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"拆部窗口機出嚟難唔難？有咩注意？"},{"pid":"fbc2d90169ac7d46bd95df6601e14d45b4e77321","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2deef7de40ee0a5f36560843c672148c47533119","tid":2505493,"uid":72316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"拆部窗口機出嚟難唔難？有咩注意？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"睇你幾大匹數<br />\n1.5匹打下，可以一個人，兩張梯，一級一級落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.5匹 50-60kg上下<br />\n正常就兩個人<br />\n不過而家真係裝機嗰啲，都係一個人，用電積升上去<br />\n人工貴"},{"pid":"73abaf0d9e50ec15c5b46fa654c0b4d9cc166f35","tid":2505493,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:06:06.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5398f638348727492c460ef006d142ef8c86080a","tid":2505493,"uid":48212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"水壓機邊到買"},{"pid":"750ced3275f92a052fd9a482fdf2811c5156579d","tid":2505493,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"窗口機無洗開真係唔好洗啦(1,2年先1次搵人洗好過)<br />\n<br />\n有d生手又唔知邊d位唔濕得 <br />\n<br />\n再唔係就洗完部機勁嘈就無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b16806389dcfed06e658efda04064843167f669","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5398f638348727492c460ef006d142ef8c86080a","tid":2505493,"uid":48212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"水壓機邊到買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:23:52.000Z","msg":"貴野-&gt;上海街<br />\n2匹歐洲機$4000 full set連動L咀<br />\n<br />\n相中德國k記，支那買平XG一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e18f5f9fd861adbf371e1dc650dbbc9d031d829","tid":2505493,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"750ced3275f92a052fd9a482fdf2811c5156579d","tid":